---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
const wasteAidTechStack = [
    {
        src: "./logos/next.png",
        alt: "Nextjs",
    },
    {
        src: "./logos/tw.png",
        alt: "Tailwind CSS",
    },
    {
        src: "./logos/trpc.png",
        alt: "tRPC",
    },
    {
        src: "./logos/next-auth.png",
        alt: "Next-Auth",
    },
    {
        src: "./logos/prisma.png",
        alt: "Prisma",
    },
    {
        src: "./logos/mysql.png",
        alt: "MySQL",
    },
    {
        src: "./logos/ts.png",
        alt: "TypeScript",
    },
]
---

<Layout title="Keval Mistry">
    <main class="max-w-[700px] px-5 py-20 mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Hi ðŸ‘‹</h1>
        <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold">I'm Keval</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 leading-6">
            And I'm just a guy who's into programming, more specifically web
            development. I've been working in the web development space for more
            than 2 years individually and for 1 year professionally. My
            strongest point is frontend, and (yeah, you guessed it right!) I
            specialize in React and its ecosystem. I also take part in backend
            tasks from time to time, and in 2024, one of my goals is to learn
            more about backend development that scales. Also, I'm a big
            developer experience and tooling enthusiast; I love seeing low-level
            languages like Rust and Go penetrating this space.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-40">
            <p class="text-2xl font-medium">Work Experience</p>
            <div class="w-full border-t mb-6 border-gray-500"></div>

            <div class="pl-2">
                <p
                    class="text-3xl font-medium flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap"
                >
                    1. CultureX Entertaiment Pvt. Lmt.
                </p>
                <p class="font-light italic text-gray-200 text-sm">
                    30-Jan-23 to 31-Jul-23 Â· Internship | 01-Aug-23 to Present Â·
                    Full-Time
                </p>
                <span
                    class="bg-[#4d4d4d] mt-1 w-fit px-2 rounded-full pb-0.5 text-base flex items-center justify-center font-normal"
                    >Frontend Developer</span
                >

                <div
                    class="pl-[1px] mt-4 ml-2 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#4d4d4d] from-75% to-transparent to-100%"
                >
                    <div class="list-disc bg-[#111] text-gray-200">
                        <p class="relative pl-3 mb-2">
                            <span
                                class="absolute w-[7px] -left-[4px] h-[7px] rounded-full top-2 bg-[#4d4d4d]"
                            ></span>
                            I had joined CulturX as frontend intern where my job
                            was to transform Figma designs into production ready
                            UI with Reactjs
                        </p>
                        <p class="relative pl-3 mb-2">
                            <span
                                class="absolute w-[7px] -left-[4px] h-[7px] rounded-full top-2 bg-[#4d4d4d]"
                            ></span>
                            As time went i took many responsibilies and have done
                            some prominent things:
                        </p>
                        <p class="relative pl-3 mb-2">
                            <span
                                class="absolute w-[7px] -left-[4px] h-[7px] rounded-full top-2 bg-[#4d4d4d]"
                            ></span>
                            I migrated company's two CRA (create-react-app) projects
                            to vite and increased development build speed by 10-100x
                            and production build speed by 2x
                        </p>
                        <p class="relative pl-3 mb-2">
                            <span
                                class="absolute w-[7px] -left-[4px] h-[7px] rounded-full top-2 bg-[#4d4d4d]"
                            ></span>
                            I migrated project from bootstrap to Tailwind which allowed
                            us to develop UI at much faster pace & also allowed us
                            to use tailwind dependent UI solutions like Shad-cn
                        </p>
                        <p class="relative pl-3 mb-2">
                            <span
                                class="absolute w-[7px] -left-[4px] h-[7px] rounded-full top-2 bg-[#4d4d4d]"
                            ></span>
                            I created a micro-service to generate PDF file by leveraging
                            packages like puppetear & React which looks like this
                            & this
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-40">
            <p class="text-2xl font-medium">Personal Projects</p>
            <div class="w-full border-t mb-10"></div>

            <div
                class="border-2 rounded-lg border-[#4d4d4d] bg-[#4d4d4d20] py-2 px-3"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <p class="text-xl font-medium flex-1">Waste-Aid</p>
                    <div
                        class="flex h-[35px] w-full flex-1 items-center justify-end"
                    >
                        {
                            wasteAidTechStack.map((item, idx) => (
                                <div
                                    class={`group relative z-[${10 - idx}] -ml-3 h-[34px] w-[34px] rounded-full border-2 transition-all hover:z-20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-110`}
                                >
                                    <img
                                        src={item.src}
                                        alt={item.alt}
                                        class={`object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0`}
                                    />
                                    <span class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-max -translate-x-1/2 rounded bg-gray-600 p-0 px-1.5 text-xs opacity-0 transition-all group-hover:-top-full group-hover:opacity-100">
                                        {item.alt}
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            ))
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-gray-200 text-sm">
                    Waste-Aid is open marketplace for recycler and waste
                    donators
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
